{"title":"ubuntu传递文件","uid":"19cf9e74e14a2517a8a76662983565e7","slug":"ubuntu拖拽文件","date":"2023-10-13T01:17:12.000Z","updated":"2023-10-13T01:26:50.829Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ubuntu拖拽文件.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>在安装完Ubuntu后想传输文件非常的麻烦</p>\n<p>网上查阅教程大多都说安装完VMware tools 后便可自由拖拽文件，但安装完后并不行</p>\n<p>查阅发现从Ubuntu14.04开始open-vm-tools 代替了官方 VMware Tools，所以应该改安装open-vm-tools。</p>\n<p>#步骤</p>\n<p>##<strong>1.打开Ubuntu的设置页面，打开关于-软件更新，更改下载自：来自中国的服务器，关闭窗口，重启Ubuntu。</strong></p>\n<p>##2.<strong>打开终端，输入sudo apt-get install open-vm-tools-desktop，根据提示完成安装后应该能观察到页面自动调整了大小，此时说明安装成功。重新启动便可拖拽传输文件</strong></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"在安装完Ubuntu后想传输文件非常的麻烦 网上查阅教程大多都说安装完VMware tools 后便可自由拖拽文件，但安装完后并不行 查阅发现从Ubuntu14...","permalink":"/post/ubuntu拖拽文件","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":303,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"教程","slug":"教程","count":2,"path":"api/tags/教程.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"SoldAllFruit","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"SZU/IC-Studying...","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/fruit-lxe","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"markdowm语法","uid":"9e5f64992b23fad3292f9a368c78148e","slug":"markdowm语法","date":"2023-10-10T11:02:28.000Z","updated":"2023-10-13T01:26:13.950Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/markdowm语法.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"@TOC 欢迎使用Markdown编辑器你好！ 这是你第一次使用 Markdown编辑器 所展示的欢迎页。如果你想学习如何使用Markdown编辑器, 可以仔细...","permalink":"/post/markdowm语法","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.4k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"author":{"name":"SoldAllFruit","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"SZU/IC-Studying...","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/fruit-lxe","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn